Story: 10 - Shinsekai Yori utilizes gradual pacing and multiple time skips to tell one of the most thought-provoking stories I've ever encountered. I'm going to refrain from mentioning any specific plot details because the less you know going into this series, the better it is. The series is split into three distinct acts: childhood, teenage years, and\
