    Shinsekai Yori is probably one of the better releases the anime community has seen over the last couple of years. Initial impressions are rather timid. It reads like a checklist of mainstream-but-not-so-mainstream fare.\
Set in the future? Check.\
Humans? Check.\
Very few of the above left alive? Check.\
Implied (and later verified) apocalypse? Check.\
Superhuman powers? Check.\
Weird beings? Check.\
Surrealist art, decent music and good production? Check.\
