Shinsekai Yori is gonna be a huge mess to criticize. I'm as polarised as can be since the anime is both a diamond in the rough and complete and unabated mess. I myself don't even know how I really feel about this. I was bored and annoyed at so many things and then the ending almost entirely made up for every single bad part of it(something which I never say).\
